  "description": {
    "zh": "军事基地之旅，嗯，你感兴趣吗？\n\n那太好了！我听说那里十分热门还极具危险。这里目前被一帮退役的海军陆战队疯子占领了，剩余的其他地区也被其他Raider掠夺者蚕食着。据说里面有食物、药品、军事装备甚至一些高端电子设备——足够在任何情况甚至核战争中生存下来。显然，在那儿重要的建筑上都会画着国际象棋的棋子进行标记用于识别。你能去看看这些地方吗？看看它们是否对我们有用。探查完后回来，确保平安离开那里。",
    "en": "Trip to the military base, you interested by any chance?\n\nThe place is extremely hot, really dangerous. Some maniac ex-marine and his gang controls most of the area, the rest is controlled by raiders. People say that it contains supplies like food, medication, military equipment and high tier electronics. Enough to survive a nuclear war. Apparently the important buildings have chess-figures painted onto them.\n\nCan you check those out? Lets see if any of them have any use for us. Come back when you took a look at them and make sure to leave the place in one piece."
  },
